              "id": "QUE58887",
              "question": "Justin and his parents are driving from Georgia to Pennsylvania to settle Justin into his new college dorm. Shortly after they arrive in Pennsylvania, the members of the Thyme family are surprised to find that they are passing unusual horse-drawn buggies traveling on the road. Glancing back, they notice that the women in the buggies are wearing bonnets and long dresses and that the men have beards but no moustaches. Confused, Justin taps his mother on the shoulder and asks, “Are we in the middle of an episode of \n\u003cem\u003eFringe\u003c/em\u003e?” In sociological terms, Justin is experiencing __________.\n\u003cbr /\u003e",
